data.title: Mega Ramp Racing Set
data.description:
The Kidkraft Mega Ramp Racing Set gives young kids an awesome one-stop shop for all of their favorite toy cars. It’s a speedy ramp, a parking garage, an elevator, a car wash and a gas station all in one convenient package! The centerpiece of this jumbo-sized racing set is its three-level “Mega Ramp,”  which launches cars high in the air after they build up momentum. There’s even a launch pad that kids lower to let the cars go, guaranteeing that they take off at the same time. Features include: 
*Three lights – green, yellow and red – that help countdown to the beginning of race time 
*Gliding elevator takes passengers to the top of the parking garage
*Three-level “Mega Ramp” with launch pad for racing cars against one another
*Three-level spiral ramp
*Helicopter and helipad
*Car wash with moving brushes
*Five vehicles
*Gas station

Dimensions: 34.88"L x 16"W x 22.38"H
Materials: MDF, Plastic
Country of Origin: China

data.title: KidKraft Aero City Train Set & Table
data.description:
Let’s play pretend! The Aero City Train Set & Table puts a busy city at your child’s fingertips. It’s so much fun to push vehicles up and down the track, fly the airplane over the city and help the fire department put out dangerous fires. Features include:
*Combines a train table with a 85-piece train set
*Long, winding track that can be put together in an endless number of ways 
*Deluxe molded mountain and a tall hospital with helipad
* Roundabout turntable piece moves 360° so vehicles can change directions
*Police station and fire station with molded plastic roofs
*Three train cars, a fire truck, a police car, a helicopter, a bulldozer, and an airplane
*Smiling townspeople, trees, trees and construction cones
*Table keeps play time off the floor and closer to eye level
*Smart, sturdy construction
*Four plastic storage bins
*Packaged with detailed, step-by-step assembly instructions
*Made of composite wood materials with molded plastic
*Train track is compatible with all KidKraft, Brio® and Thomas & Friends™ Wooden Railway vehicles and play sets
